theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("0_font")
text = "We hope you've learned more local networks and short supply chains. These shorter networks have a higher resilience to outside factors, such as COVID-19.

While this game showcased this on a large scale, our daily lives can also be affected by it. When we choose to support local businesses and buy small, our actions do have tangible benefits to our communities.

"
